#include<iostream>
#include<stdio.h>
#include<map>
#include<string>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
    int n,q;
    string trueName,newName,query;
    map<string,string> nameLink;
    cin>>n>>q;  
    while(n--)
    {
        cin>>trueName>>newName;
        nameLink.insert(make_pair(newName,trueName));
    }
    while(q--)
    {
        cin>>query;
        if(nameLink.count(query))
            cout<<nameLink[query]<<"\n";
        else
            cout<<"Name not found\n";
    }
}
